{"word":"G3551 - νόμος - nómos - nom'-os - Law","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">νόμος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">nómos</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">nom'-os</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Law</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Noun Masculine / பெயர்ச்சொல் (ஆண்பால்)</span>"},{"paragraph":"நியாயப்பிரமாணம், வேதம், வேதப்பிரமாணம் - ஆண்பால் பெயர்ச்சொல்"},{"paragraph":"anything established, anything received by usage, a custom, usage, law a command, law"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From a primary word <b>&#x03BD;&#x03B5;&#x0301;&#x03BC;&#x03C9;</b> <b>nemo&#x0304;</b> (to <i>parcel</i> out, especially <i>food</i> or <i>grazing</i> to animals); <i>law</i> (through the idea of prescriptive <i>usage</i>), generally (<i>regulation</i>), specifically (of Moses [including the volume]; also of the Gospel), or figuratively (a <i>principle</i>): - law.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G1772/1772\">G1772</a>, <a href=\"#/G3544/3544\">G3544</a>, <a href=\"#/G3545/3545\">G3545</a>, <a href=\"#/G3547/3547\">G3547</a>, <a href=\"#/G3548/3548\">G3548</a>, <a href=\"#/G3549/3549\">G3549</a>, <a href=\"#/G3550/3550\">G3550</a>, <a href=\"#/G3551/3551\">G3551</a>, <a href=\"#/G3891/3891\">G3891</a>, <a href=\"#/G3892/3892\">G3892</a>, <a href=\"#/G458/458\">G458</a>, <a href=\"#/G459/459\">G459</a>, <a href=\"#/G460/460\">G460</a>"}]}